4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed to prepare individuals for a career in cybersecurity, regardless of prior experience. The program spans 16 weeks and includes 3 live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. Students will gain foundational knowledge in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, alongside practical skills in cloud security, penetration testing, and threat intelligence analysis. Participants will also learn risk management through data loss prevention and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop